Alan Witkowski

** Building **

- Ogre3D -
	http://www.ogre3d.org/download/sdk

	Add OGRE_HOME environment variable that points to the SDK root directory (e.g. C:\OgreSDK)

- Bullet Physics -
	https://code.google.com/p/bullet/downloads/list

	Add BULLET_ROOT environment variable that points to the SDK root directory (e.g. C:\BulletSDK)

	Use cmake to build bullet. Build in the same directory as BULLET_ROOT.
	If built correctly, .lib files should be ${BULLET_ROOT}/libs/Debug and ${BULLET_ROOT}/libs/Release